Interface Vehicle

All Superinterfaces:
Comparable<Vehicle>
All Known Implementing Classes:
DangerousTruck, FoodTruck
public interface Vehicle extends Comparable<Vehicle>
The Vehicle interface represents a generic vehicle that can be used for transportation. It extends the Comparable interface to enable comparison between vehicles based on their carrying capacity.
